    <section>
      <p>ICEBERG stands apart in the nicotine pouch landscape. Where other brands chase mainstream appeal, ICEBERG leans into extremity—extreme strength, extreme flavour boldness, extreme niche appeal. Manufactured by Neoptolem (Poland), this brand has become the go-to choice for experienced users who don't just want nicotine; they want an uncompromising, aggressive nicotine experience with flavours that don't whisper but shout.</p>
      <p>Unlike brands that try to be everything to everyone, ICEBERG has a crystal-clear target audience: people who've graduated from mild pouches and actively seek the strongest options available. With 13 products spanning 6mg to 40mg, it's the most comprehensive ultra-strength lineup at SnusFriend.</p>
      <p>This guide covers ICEBERG's complete range, its fearless approach to strength and flavour, the philosophy behind its positioning, and honest guidance on safe, responsible use at these extreme concentrations.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>ICEBERG Brand History</h2>
      <p>ICEBERG is manufactured by Neoptolem, a Polish company that entered the European nicotine market with a bold thesis: most manufacturers are playing it too safe. The 'ultra-strength' market was underserved—users wanted the absolute strongest pouches available, not more cucumber-mint varieties for entry-level consumers.</p>
      <p>Neoptolem's response was ICEBERG: a brand with no apologies, no compromises, and no attempts to appeal to beginners. Every product line, every flavour decision, every strength option was optimized for one audience: experienced, strength-seeking nicotine users.</p>
      <p>The brand's genesis traces back to Russia (Neoptolem's original market), but ICEBERG has expanded aggressively across the EU, particularly in Poland, the UK, and Scandinavia. Today, it competes directly with established extreme-strength competitors like Siberia and Pablo, but with a crucial differentiator: flavour diversity. While Siberia focuses almost exclusively on minimalist mint, ICEBERG offers berry, fruit, and sweet variants alongside its icy arsenal.</p>
      <p>This positioning—ultra-strength plus flavour variety—has made ICEBERG a cult favourite among experienced users who want both intensity and taste complexity.</p>
    </section>

