      <p>ICEBERG represents a philosophy: strength without apology, diversity without dilution, quality without compromise. In a market where many brands chase mainstream acceptance, ICEBERG doubles down on its core audience—experienced, strength-seeking nicotine users who don't settle for mediocrity.</p>
      <p>With 13 active products at SnusFriend spanning 6mg to 40mg and covering mint, berry, fruit, and sweet profiles, ICEBERG offers the most comprehensive ultra-strength range available. Whether you're an experienced user exploring flavour options within the 30mg tier, or a hardened veteran testing the 40mg Ultra tier, ICEBERG has a product engineered for your needs.</p>
      <p>But this is not casual territory. Every ICEBERG pouch demands respect, self-awareness about your nicotine tolerance, and commitment to safe, responsible use. A 40mg pouch is not a typical consumer product—it's a vehicle for experienced users seeking specific, intense nicotine delivery.</p>
      <p>If you're ready for ICEBERG, start with 6mg in a familiar flavour, assess your tolerance over a week, and only progress to higher strengths after you understand your individual response. And if you're entirely new to nicotine pouches, please choose a gentler brand first.</p>
